For the price we paid and the amount of time we spent in our room this was a great deal.	But it's efficient, clean, well designed, in a great location and a great value at $139/night.	Overall I would recommend this hotel for the location and the price.	If you want to spend all day in a bigger room go and stay at a bog-standard chain hotel and pay twice the price.	The service was perfect and the price, for some reason, is much better than many of the chain hotels in the area.